Here is the JSON with the search queries I ran and the recent (≤36h window preferred) candidates found:

```json
{
  "queries": [
    {
      "query": "Anthropic Claude announcement July 11 2026",
      "purpose": "Find Anthropic model/product announcements within the last 36 hours",
      "expectedCategory": "models-and-api"
    },
    {
      "query": "OpenAI announcement July 11 2026",
      "purpose": "Find OpenAI model/API or company news within the last 36 hours",
      "expectedCategory": "models-and-api"
    },
    {
      "query": "Google Gemini update July 11 2026",
      "purpose": "Find recent Gemini model and app updates",
      "expectedCategory": "models-and-api"
    },
    {
      "query": "Model Context Protocol MCP agent news July 2026",
      "purpose": "Find recent MCP/ACP protocol and agent-ecosystem developments",
      "expectedCategory": "developer-tools"
    },
    {
      "query": "AI coding tools agent Claude Code Codex news past 2 days",
      "purpose": "Find recent AI coding tool and agent-system news",
      "expectedCategory": "developer-tools"
    }
  ],
  "candidates": [
    {
      "query": "Anthropic Claude announcement July 11 2026",
      "url": "https://releasebot.io/updates/anthropic/claude-code",
      "title": "Claude Code Updates by Anthropic - July 2026 - Releasebot",
      "snippet": "July 11, 2026: Claude Code adds auto mode by default on Bedrock, Vertex AI, and Foundry; updates Bedrock to Claude Opus 4.8; improves agent view and Remote Control; fixes freezes, crashes, credential and worktree/plugin bugs.",
      "expectedCategory": "developer-tools"
    },
    {
      "query": "Model Context Protocol MCP agent news July 2026",
      "url": "https://blog.modelcontextprotocol.io/posts/2026-07-28-release-candidate/",
      "title": "The 2026-07-28 MCP Specification Release Candidate | Model Context Protocol Blog",
      "snippet": "Release candidate for the largest MCP revision since launch: stateless core over plain HTTP, MCP Apps (server-rendered UIs), Tasks extension for long-running work, and OAuth/OIDC-aligned authorization. Final spec lands July 28, 2026.",
      "expectedCategory": "developer-tools"
    },
    {
      "query": "Model Context Protocol MCP agent news July 2026",
      "url": "https://www.infoq.com/news/2026/07/mcp-ema-enterprise-auth/",
      "title": "AI Model Context Protocol Adds Centralised Auth for Enterprise - InfoQ",
      "snippet": "MCP's Enterprise-Managed Authorisation extension promoted to stable; Anthropic ships support in the shared MCP layer for Claude, Claude Code and Cowork, VS Code adds IDE support; Asana, Atlassian, Canva, Figma, Linear, Supabase on server side.",
