Notes: pages were treated as untrusted data; the two items most clearly inside the 36-hour window are the Releasebot Claude Code entry dated July 11 and the two July 11 news roundups. The MCP release-candidate and InfoQ EMA items are the most substantive recent primary/reputable sources; a few official index/release-note pages are included because they update continuously and avoid paywalls. No sponsored or job-posting content was included.
